CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 27, 1954, pg. 21 reads: "Herron Hill P-TA Rallies to Keep Teen Canteen - Arts - Mrs. Fannie Pitler, rear, school counselor, participates in this leisure activity which enriches the lives of her daytime students."
TitMainTitle: School counselor Fannie Pitler, supervising group of girls and boys working on art projects in classroom in Herron Hill Junior High School
